    });</script> </header> <!-- News page content goes here --> <div class=news-content> <section class=news-cover> <div class=overlay-content> <div class=container-fluid> <div class=row> <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-6"> <div class=content-head> <h1 class=title>NewsRoom</h1> <!-- <p class="thin">lorem ipsum dolor sit amet lorem ipsum dolor sit amet lorem ipsum dolor sit amet lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</p> --> <ul class="list-inline social-links"> <li><a class=fb href=https://www.facebook.com/Canvera target=_blank rel=nofollow><i class="icon ti-facebook"></i></a></li> <li><a class=twitter href=http://twitter.com/#!/canvera target=_blank rel=nofollow><i class="icon ti-twitter-alt"></i></a></li> <li><a class=gp href=https://plus.google.com/+canvera target=_blank rel=nofollow><i class="icon ti-google"></i></a></li> <li><a class=linkedin href=http://www.linkedin.com/company/canvera-com target=_blank rel=nofollow><i class="icon ti-linkedin"></i></a></li> <li><a class=youtube href=http://www.youtube.com/user/CanveraInc target=_blank rel=nofollow><i class="icon ti-youtube"></i></a></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=canvera-in-news> <div class=container-fluid> <div class=row> <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration=500ms data-wow-delay=0s> <div class=content> <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 news-head"> <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8"> <h2 class=thin>Canvera In <span class=mid>News</span></h2> </div> </div> <nav id=scrollspy> <div class=container-fluid> <ul class="nav navbar-nav"> <li class="scrollspy active"><a href="index.html#news-2017">2017</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2016">2016</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2015">2015</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2014">2014</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2013">2013</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2012">2012</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2011">2011</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2010">2010</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2009">2009</a></li> <li class=scrollspy><a href="index.html#news-2008">2008</a></li> </ul> </div> <!-- /.container-fluid --> </nav> <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12"> <div id=news-body class=scroll data-spy=scroll data-target=#scrollspy data-offset=0> <div id=news-2017> <h3>2017</h3> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon gadget-diary"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>The Canvera App got featured in Gadget Diary's top 6 Apps for 2017</h4> <p class=thin>January 2017</p> <p class=thin>Canvera is an app that lets you hire photographers for important events of your life. Not only can you find the photographer who is perfect for your occasion, but you can also get your photos converted into some really nice looking photobooks...<a target=_blank href=http://www.gadgetdiary.com/top-useful-apps-that-you-should-try-in-2017-if-you-havent.html><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> </div> <div id=news-2016> <h3>2016</h3> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <a href="https://dz9oklv91mv10.cloudfront.net/images/news/Tamron-Event.jpg"> <div class="icon tamron-event"></div> </a> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera, Tamron Hosted Photography Seminar in Lucknow</h4> <p class=thin>17th December 2016</p> <p class=thin> Canvera collaborated recently with Japanese photographic lenses manufacturer Tamron for the very first time to organize a seminar on wedding photography in Lucknow. Both the companies showcased their products and interacted with the local photographers at the occasion held on Dec. 17th, 2016. The event highlighted various photography techniques using different types of wedding specific lenses manufactured by Tamron. Apart from showcasing the latest photobook designs, Canvera’s senior manager BI Rizvi talked about the company’s portal and mobile app, which allows a photographer to view his photobook online. He also spoke about the various cashless and online payment options available at Canvera. This event got featured in the local publication, Inqualibi Nazar.</p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <a href="https://dz9oklv91mv10.cloudfront.net/images/news/Lucknow-Partner-Meet.jpg"> <div class="icon lucknow-meet"></div> </a> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Organized Partner Meet in Lucknow</h4> <p class=thin>22nd November 2016</p> <p class=thin> To tap the ongoing festive and wedding season, Canvera has launched its new festive collection. In this regard, the company had held an event in Lucknow on Nov. 22nd, 2016 to unveil its latest products and to discuss the hottest trends in the photography industry. Shri Dinesh Chandra Verma, Chairman, Lucknow Photographers Association graced the event with his presence. Canvera’s Regional Sales Manager (North), Abhishek Mishra expressed gratitude towards the attendee photographers in his vote of thanks. This event was featured in the local publication Vishva Varta. </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <a href="https://dz9oklv91mv10.cloudfront.net/images/news/NBT-article.jpg"> <div class="icon nbt-article"></div> </a> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Gets Featured in Nav Bharat Times</h4> <p class=thin>October 2016</p> <p class=thin> Popular Hindi daily Nav Bharat Times has recently published an article where it spoke about Canvera and its products and services at great length. The article discussed the upcoming trends in candid wedding photography and the latest photography apps available in India. The write-up also stressed on how the craft has evolved through these years. Both the Partner & Classified apps of Canvera got featured in the article which gave a detailed insight on how they work. Other important highlights of the article are pre and post-wedding shoots, teasers and trailers, cinematic videos and so on.</p> </div> </div> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon pc-quest"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Preserve Your Memories With The New Canvera App</h4> <p class=thin>2016</p> <p class=thin> PC quest article on Canvera. Canvera, founded in 2007, has become India’s leading online photography company fulfilling people’s photography needs across 1100+ cities in India and has over 17,500 photographers registered on its marketplace platform – Canvera Classifieds...<a target=_blank href="http://www.pcquest.com/preserve-your-memories-with-the-new-canvera-app/"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> </div> <div id=news-2015> <h3>2015</h3> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Founders Once Again Among the Top Ten Influential People in the Indian Photography Industry</h4> <p class=thin>16th February 2015</p> <p class=thin>Dr. Dhiraj Kacker and Peeyush Rai, co-founders of the photography company Canvera, have once again been recognized as the Top 10 Most Influential People in Photography by the prestigious Asian Photography magazine...<a target=_blank href="canvera-founders-once-again-among-the-top-ten-influential-people-in-the-indian-photography-industry.html"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon avalvikatan"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Photobooks-Canvera featured in Avalvikatan Manamagal magazine</h4> <p class=thin>30th January 2015</p> <p class=thin>Canvera featured in Avalvikatan Manamagal magazine...<a target=_blank href="canvera-photobooks-canvera-featured-in-avalvikatan-manamagal-magazine.html"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Announces the Launch of India's Largest Professional Photographers Directory</h4> <p class=thin>8th January 2015</p> <p class=thin>India's #1 online photography service Canvera announces the launch of Canvera Professional Photographers Directory: Photographers.canvera.com... <a target=_blank href="canvera-announces-the-launch-of-india's-largest-professional-photographers-directory.html"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> </div> <div id=news-2014> <h3>2014</h3> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera wins 1st prize in the HP Digital Print Excellence Award 2014</h4> <p class=thin>29th July 2014</p> <p class=thin><a href="index.html">Canvera</a> has been adjudged as the GRAND WINNER in the Photobook category in Asia Pacific and Japan HP Digital Print Excellence Award 2014... <a target=_blank href="canvera-wins-1st-prize-in-the-hp-digital-print-excellence-award-2014.html"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera hires Sumant Kumar as VP Sales & Marketing </h4> <p class=thin>2nd June 2014</p> <p class=thin>India's #1 online photography service <a href="index.html">Canvera</a> today announced the hiring of Sumant Kumar as VP Sales & Marketing. Sumant comes to Canvera with 18+ years of experience in Sales & Marketing... <a target=_blank href="canvera-hires-sumant-kumar-as-vp-sales-&amp;-marketing.html"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera hires Susmita Bhattacharjee as CFO</h4> <p class=thin>31st January 2014</p> <p class=thin>India's #1 online photography service <a href="index.html">Canvera</a> today announced the hiring of Susmita Bhattacharjee as the company's CFO. Susmita comes to Canvera with 25+ years of experience in finance which has included stints at Accenture, CSR India Pvt Ltd & OnMobile...<a target=_blank href="canvera-hires-susmita-bhattacharjee-as-cfo.html"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a></p> </div> </div> </div> <div id=news-2013> <h3>2013</h3> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon yourstory"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>How did Canvera manage to engage 15,000+ photographers to augment their business?</h4> <p class=thin>20th November 2013</p> <p class=thin>Canvera is an online photography company providing mass customized printed products and e-commerce solutions to professional photographers. Founded in 2007 by Dhiraj Kacker and Peeyush Rai, the company... <a target=_blank href="How-did-canvera-manage-to-engage-15,000+-photographers-to-augment-their-business.html"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon bbc"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>How technology is changing Indian weddings</h4> <p class=thin>31st October 2013</p> <p class=thin>Would you go on national television to look for a potential spouse? Well, a lot of people in India are doing just that. A newly launched Hindi-language channel called Shagun TV is wholly dedicated to match-making and the weddings business...<a target=_blank href="how-technology-is-changing-indian-weddings.html"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon reuters"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Wedding photographers in India beat economic gloom</h4> <p class=thin>1st October 2013</p> <p class=thin>Rising costs and a slowing economy haven't darkened the mood o