</div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera: IIT graduates' venture offers print & e-commerce solutions to photographers: The Economic Times</h4> <p class=thin>17th December 2012</p> <p class=thin>Building a business venture from a hobby is a tried and tested route. So, given that I and my business partner, Peeyush Rai, are passionate shutterbugs, it made sense to combine forces to launch Canvera.com, an online photography company, which provides mass customised printed products and e-commerce solutions for professionals. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_iitgraduatesventure"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon tech-circle"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Five things that clicked for online photography company Canvera in its latest fundraising: techcircle.in</h4> <p class=thin>28th August 2012</p> <p class=thin>It’s a difficult fundraising environment right now. Especially when it’s a Series B round, the exercise gets even tougher. Unless you have a strong revenue traction and a clear path to profitability, the money will not come by at this stage. So what really helped the online photography company Canvera Digital Technologies Pvt Ltd raise $6.5 million or Rs 35 crore in a Series B round of funding from a discerning investor like Info Edge (India) Ltd.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_fivethingsthatclicked"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Info Edge invests $6.5M in Canvera</h4> <p class=thin>28 August 2012</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com, India’s leading online photography company, today announced that Info Edge, owner of Naukri.com, made an investment of $6.5M (Rs35CR) in the company. Info Edge has made a number of investments previously in companies such as Zomato, Meritnation, MyDala, PolicyBazaar, 99labels etc but this is their largest investment to date. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_infoedgeinvestsincanvera"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Bala Parthasarathy, Co-Founder of Snapfish, joins Canvera’s Board</h4> <p class=thin>15th February 2012</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com, India’s leading online photography company, today announced that Bala Parthasarathy, one of the Co-Founders of Snapfish, has joined Canvera’s board as an advisor. Bala founded Snapfish in 1999 and was with the company through its acquisition by District Photo and an eventual sale to Hewlett-Packard. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_balajoinscanvera"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> </div> <div id=news-2011> <h3>2011</h3> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera launches “Recommend a Photographer” service</h4> <p class=thin>3rd October 2011</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com, India’s leading online photography company, today launched a unique service to connect consumers and businesses with professional photographers. This service called “Recommend a Photographer” allows anyone looking to hire professionals to specify their needs on Canvera.com.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_referaphotographer"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera runner up in APJ Photobook competition </h4> <p class=thin>25th August 2011</p> <p class=thin>Singapore: Canvera.com was first runner up at the recently concluded 2011 Asia Pacific & Japan HP Digital Print Award's Photobook competition. This is the 3rd time in 4 years that Canvera has been one of the winning teams having won the award previously in 2008 and 2009.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_runnerup_apj"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Announces the Launch of an e-commerce and Social Platform for Photographers</h4> <p class=thin>15th June 2011</p> <p class=thin>Canvera announces the launch of Canvera Vivyo, an e-commerce and social platform for photographers. Vivyo enables photographers to leverage the internet for marketing and selling their work, and to collaborate with their clients through an online hosted solution.<a href="http://www.businesswireindia.com/PressRelease.asp?b2mid=27232"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon economics-times"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Capturing Pictures, Business: The Economic Times</h4> <p class=thin>15th April 2011</p> <p class=thin>When cricketing great Anil Kumble, who is also an avid photographer, wanted to preserve the memories of his 20 year cricket career, he turned to Bangalore-based online photography start-up Canvera Digital Technologies. Kumble recently got a coffee table book done from Canvera.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_capturing_pictures_business"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Digital Focus: Canvera – A tale of digital that inspires: PrintWeek</h4> <p class=thin>5th April 2011</p> <p class=thin>Dhiraj Kacker, the CEO of Canvera, was 35 when he began Canvera with his friend and IIT batchmate Peeyush Rai. As they made the decision to establish their own business, Kacker and his wife quit their jobs in the United States and moved to Bengaluru to begin the venture they were going to call Canvera. Kacker had worked in the digital imaging and photography industry for 19 years. He holds a PhD in Electrical Engineering with specialisation in Image and Signal Processing, and had worked in one of the United States' leading digital imaging services: Shutterfly.com. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_canvera_a_tale_of_digital_that_inspires"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Shakes Up Photography Market; Ecomm Platform On The Cards: techcircle.in</h4> <p class=thin>8th March 2011</p> <p class=thin>After entering the market with printing of wedding albums, Canvera, a Bangalore-based digital imaging firm, is now leveraging its technology infrastructure to offer more to the photographer community. It is now launching an e-commerce platform for photographers called Vivyo.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=canvera_shakes_up_photography"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon hp"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>HP Provides Jump-start for Canvera's Success: Business Wire</h4> <p class=thin>7th March 2011</p> <p class=thin>PALO ALTO, Calif.--(BUSINESS WIRE)--HP (NYSE:HPQ) today announced that Canvera, India's first nationally branded professional imaging service provider, has selected HP solutions and services for delivering consistent, high-quality printing services to customers.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=hp_provides_jump_start"><span class="thin read">Read More </span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon mydigitalfc"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>All yours for a crore: mydigitalfc.com</h4> <p class=thin>3rd February 2011</p> <p class=thin>Not very long ago wedding photography was just a black and white affair with enthusiastic relatives wielding unwieldy film SLRs. But things have changed with photographers being paid up to Rs 1 crore to cover a single wedding.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_all_yours_for_a_crore"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Case Study: How Canvera leveraged credit line from HP Financials Services </h4> <p class=thin>January 2011</p> <p class=thin>The demand for professional photography in India is enormous with weddings driving more than half the industry. One factor is the demographics. India has over 1.1 billion people and is a young country—half of its population is under 25 years of age. Around 10 million couples get married every year <a href="https://www.canvera.com/static/documents/How_Canvera_Leveraged_Credit_Line_From_HP_Financials_Services_Jan_2011.pdf"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon photo-fair"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera coverage by Asian Photography's Show Daily, Photofair</h4> <p class=thin>6th January 2011</p> <p class=thin>Canvera, the online photobooks and album printing company for professional photographers and consumers alike, looks poised to take on the new year with newer challenges and opportunities supported by their effective business model. We quizzed Dr. Dhiraj Kacker, CEO and Co-founder, Canvera about their participation in Photofair 2011. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_bringing_photobooks_to_photofair"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>No income for nearly a year - Dhiraj Kacker: ET Wealth</h4> <p class=thin>10th January 2011</p> <p class=thin>More than 19 years of working with start-ups in digital imaging and photography. Seven US patents to show for the effort. I decided in 2007 it was time to use the experience and expertise to turn decision-maker. Around the same time, my friend and IIT batchmate Peeyush Rai presented the idea of establishing our own business. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_no_income_for_nearly_an_year"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Always at Your Service - Canvera: Smart Photography</h4> <p class=thin>7th January 2011</p> <p class=thin>With the emergence of online printing and digital photo albums, many companies are getting into this genre, and Canvera is a prominent player in this field. Mathew Thottungal converses with Dr. Dhiraj Kacker, CEO of Canvera, to find out about the company's strategies.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_always_at_your_service"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> </div> <div id=news-2010> <h3>2010</h3> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon economics-times"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>The bottom of the pyramid demands more research: Economic Times</h4> <p class=thin>26th December 2010</p> <p class=thin>What if you heard of a physician who gave you the wrong medicine? You would certaily feel disrespect and hatred for that person. The same treatment would be meted out to a tailor who took wrong measurements and gave you an ill fitting tuxedo or a chef who tried to create fusion between lavender and black pepper -- not worth the mention if you are in a laudatory mood. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_the_bottom_of_the_pyramid"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera.com wins TiE-Lumis Entrepreneurial Excellence Awards for 2010</h4> <p class=thin>22nd December 2010</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com was today declared the winner of the TiE-Lumis Entrepreneurial Excellence Awards 2010 at the TiE Entrepreneurial Summit 2010, one of the largest entrepreneurship symposium in Asia. Currently in its 3rd year, the Excellence Awards are aimed to not only recognize the idea but also the effort, innovation and passion of the entrepreneurs who have braved the odds and made a mark with their start-ups. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_entrepreneurial_award_2010"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera looks at integrating photo apps with Facebook, Twitter: MSN</h4> <p class=thin>17th December 2010</p> <p class=thin>Online and mobile photography solutions firm Canvera today said it is working on applications that will allow users to upload their photographs on social networking sites Facebook and Twitter. <a href="http://news.in.msn.com/business/article.aspx?cp-documentid=4710323"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Inside Indian e-commerce Bazaar: The Times of India</h4> <p class=thin>22nd October 2010</p> <p class=thin>As chief revenue officer in the country's first-ever low-cost airline, Air Deccan, John Kuruvilla had an unusual brief. Instead of a budget to spend on marketing activities, he had a list of items that he had to derive revenue from. This included selling advertising space, marketing food and gifts, both within and outside the aircraft. <a href=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tech/enterprise-it/strategy/Inside-Indian-e-commerce-Bazaar-/articleshow/6793147.cms><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon the-economics-times"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Customised photobooks breathe life into photo biz: The Economic Times</h4> <p class=thin>4th September 2010</p> <p class=thin>NEW DELHI: The Great Indian Wedding still has all the swish, colour, camera, lights and action, but one thing's noticeably different: The way the story is told. Memories of the event are no longer bound to garish, unwieldy photo albums that are later shipped to family. Version 2.0 of the wedding album's here, and photos are set in slick 'photobooks,' complete with visual effects and customised packaging. <a href=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/news-by-industry/et-cetera/Customised-photobooks-breathe-life-into-photo-biz/articleshow/6489707.cms><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Freeze Frame: Entrepreneur</h4> <p class=thin>July 2010</p> <p class=thin>Photos tell a story and it is only apt for stories to find their way to books. When Dhiraj Kacker and Peeyush Rai got together with a desire to start something on their own, a business around photography was the quest. While Rai was an avid photographer, Kacker had a background in digital photography, thanks to his work at US company Shutterfly, which was in the business of creating photobooks, cards and calendars.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_freeze_frame"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon business-today"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>India's hottest startups: Business Today</h4> <p class=thin>27th June 2010</p> <p class=thin>BT's hunt for promising start-ups this year unearths gems with a difference - business models that survived a recession which felled many a giant. Canvera has been selected as one of the hottest start-ups in India as part of this feature by Business Today.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_the_memory_remains"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon smart-photography"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>'Wide Angle' Review by Mathew Thottungal: Smart Photography</h4> <p class=thin>May 2010</p> <p class=thin>One of the foremost exponents of fast spin bowling and also a distinguished former India captain, Anil Kumble, is arguably one of the few cricketing legends, who has worn the Indian cap with grace, dignity and patriotism. Even though he has retired from national duties, yet his determination and aggression is still evident, in the way his leadership qualities have more than mentored the Royal Challengers of Bangalore in the IPL league.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_wideangle_review_mathew_thottungal"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera - A Digital Imaging Services Company Targeting Wedding Market Needs</h4> <p class=thin>13th April 2010</p> <p class=thin>Canvera is a Digital Photography company (HQed in Bangalore) servicing the needs of professional photographers all over India. The company's flagship products are high-end customized coffee-table-book that professional photographers buy to service markets such as weddings, fashion, private and corporate functions, corporate brand books etc. <a href="http://www.pluggd.in/wedding-photography-album-canvera-a-digital-services-company-understanding-business-model-297/"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>'Wide Angle' Review by Gulu Ezekiel</h4> <p class=thin>31st March 2010</p> <p class=thin>Apart from being India's greatest match-winning bowler, there have been very few cricketers who have worn the India cap with such grace, dignity and patriotism as Anil Kumble. It has been nearly two years since his retirement from international cricket, though he is still making his mark in the IPL.<a href="http://www.dreamcricket.com/dreamcricket/news.hspl?nid=13589&ntid=6"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Making moolah out of people's emotive memories: Deccan Herald</h4> <p class=thin>1st April 2010</p> <p class=thin>Emotions are invaluable. Thus, preserving memories attached with emotions, in a way one wants, is not inconceivable. And with photographs being the traditional and widely used medium of preserving memories in physical form, the want for customisation has always prevailed.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_deccan_herald_moolah"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Big idea: A new way of presenting photos: Brand Wagon, The Financial Express</h4> <p class=thin>23rd March 2010</p> <p class=thin>After spending over a decade and a half in the US, college buddies Dhiraj Kacker and Peeyush Rai wanted to do something of their own. They chose to set up shop in India, their own country and also, a fast growing market.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_picture_this"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>India's first Wedding Photography Awards receives a record response of over 8000 entries!</h4> <p class=thin>19th March 2010</p> <p class=thin>The Better Photography magazine in association with Kodak conducted the first ever grand scale award to recognise the 200,000+ strong wedding photographer community in India. The inaugural edition of the Kodak-Better Photography Wedding Photographer of the Year awards was being held at the Hyatt Regency, Mumbai on the 19th of March 2010. Says Madhavan Pillai, Editor, Better Photography, "Wedding photography is an oft misunderstood, oft underestimated profession.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_bp_award_response"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Mallya, Warne unveil Kumble's memoir of 'off-the-field' cricket photography: Sify.com</h4> <p class=thin>18th March 2010</p> <p class=thin>As Sachin Tendulkar relates in his Foreword, Kumble, the man with the camera, would tell his teammates, "As long as I am in the team, you will have no privacy." <a href=http://sify.com/finance/mallya-warne-unveil-kumble-s-memoir-of-off-the-field-cricket-photography-news-news-kdssOcdhfjb.html><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Talking to Anil Kumble about 'Wide Angle': MyBangalore.com </h4> <p class=thin>18th March 2010</p> <p class=thin>Spanning close to two decades, Anil Kumble's career has seen the different ups and downs of the Indian cricket. No bowler in history won India more Test matches than Anil Kumble, for the man represents the terms: match winner and a fighter.<a href=http://mybangalore.com/article/0310/talking-to-anil-kumble-about-wide-angle.html><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Warne releases Kumble's book: Yahoo! Cricket</h4> <p class=thin>18th March 2010</p> <p class=thin>Bangalore: Spin legend Shane Warne on Wednesday released Anil Kumble's book "Wide Angle" - a collection of off-field pictures shot by the former India skipper. <a href="http://cricket.yahoo.com/cricket/news/article?id=item/2.0/-/story/cricket.yahoonews.com/warne-release-kumbles-book-20100318/"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Warne releases Kumble's book: The Hindu</h4> <p class=thin>17th March 2010</p> <p class=thin>Spin legend Shane Warne on Wednesday released Anil Kumble's book 'Wide Angle' - a collection of off-field pictures shot by the former India skipper. The Australian cricketer recalled his long association with Kumble at the launch, organised at a city hotel here.<a href=http://beta.thehindu.com/sport/cricket/article253896.ece><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Kumble's Wide Angle Promises Perfect Ten: Deccan Herald</h4> <p class=thin>17th March 2010</p> <p class=thin>That there is an ace photographer lurking inside Anil Kumble has never been a secret. On Wednesday evening, his first photographic compilation, 'Wide Angle', was released at a touchingly memorable function by his great mate and fellow leg-spinner Shane Warne.<a href=http://www.deccanherald.com/content/58567/kumbles-wide-angle-promises-perfect.html><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Anil Kumble's most treasured passion exposed</h4> <p class=thin>March 2010</p> <p class=thin>Royal Challengers Bangalore proudly presents Anil Kumble's Wide Angle that brings together the great player's abiding passions - cricket, photography and wildlife. It gives a glimpse into the lives of his contemporaries beyond the boundary and our wild animals within theirs.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_wideangle1"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>The multi-million wedding album photo-op: DNA Money</h4> <p class=thin>January 2010</p> <p class=thin>Indian weddings, over the years, have been an ideal launch pad for innovative business initiatives; as in the case of IITians Dhiraj Kacker and Peeyush Rai, who started Canvera Digital Technologies, a digital imaging solutions provider. Canvera has changed the image of wedding albums, replacing bulky and heavy albums with swanky photobooks. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_dna_money_jan_2010"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera awarded "Best Innovation in Technology" for bringing Professionalism & Innovation to an unorganized market</h4> <p class=thin>January 2010</p> <p class=thin>Asian Photography magazine awarded <span class=thin><a href="index.html">Canvera.com</a> the "Best Innovation in Technology" award at their recently concluded annual awards held alongside Photofair 2010 in Mumbai. The award was given to recognize the professionalism and innovation Canvera is bringing to a highly fragmented market.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_asianphotography"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </span></p> </div> </div> </div> <div id=news-2009> <h3>2009</h3> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Record breaking 30K+ submissions on Canvera.com for Better Photography's annual contest</h4> <p class=thin>December 2009</p> <p class=thin>Online submission through <a href="index.html">www.canvera.com</a> for Better Photography's annual photography contest "Photographer of the Year" and "Young Photographer of the Year" have broken all past records for submissions. For the current year's contest more than 30K+ entries were submitted online through the specially designed microsite. <a href=http://www.canvera.com/betterphotography>www.canvera.com/betterphotography</a> in addition to about 10K+ submitted through offline channels.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=bp_record_breaking_submission"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera hires Aditya Kothari as VP of Sales </h4> <p class=thin>15th December 2009</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com, India's fastest growing online digital photography company, recently hired Aditya Kothari as Vice President of Sales. Prior to Canvera, Aditya worked as VP of Sales & Marketing at Alcan where he not only rapidly grew sales but also established Alcan as a leader in its category.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_vpsales"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera coffee-table-books chosen to present Best of Marie Claire Fashion</h4> <p class=thin>4th December 2009 </p> <p class=thin>A remarkable collaboration between Marie Claire India, the celebrated fashion magazine from the The Outlook group, and Canvera will be unveiled at the Marie Claire Made in India Fashion Awards at The Leela Kempinski in Gurgaon. Canvera will be presenting The Best of Marie Claire Fashion, a finely curated, limited-edition coffee table book of fashion images by India's famous photographers. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_marieclaire"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Industry Opinion - Dhiraj's interview with Smart Photography</h4> <p class=thin>November 2009</p> <p class=thin>Consumer spending has slowed down; it is at a much slower pace than what it was an year ago. However, it isn't surprising that photo majors have really struggled to eke out profits, or just break even, during the last couple of years. But, some photo-imaging players have managed to thrive amid the gloom and Canvera is one such classic example. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/downloadData.do?downloadContent=Dhiraj_interview_smart_photography.pdf"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Better Photography's annual contest goes online with Canvera.com</h4> <p class=thin>September 2009</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com, India's fastest growing online photography company has been chosen to be the online partner for the fifth edition of the Better Photography Photographer of the 2009 Awards. Published by Infomedia18 Ltd, Better Photography has been the leading photography magazine in India and South Asia for over twelve years now. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=betterphotography_annualcontest"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Chronicle your life on a Coffee Table: Midday</h4> <p class=thin>22nd September 2009</p> <p class=thin>An online photography company now helps you treasure the special moments in life by binding them for eternity in a coffee table book. It's yours within 48 hours of having placed the orders, and designed to remain in the family for many generations to indulge and enjoy.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_midday"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Supports Anand Seth's Photography Show</h4> <p class=thin>August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Committed to setting new photography standards, Canvera - India's fastest growing digital photography company - recently hosted a photography exhibition for ace lensmen Anand Seth at Cibo. Saluting beautiful women achievers, Canvera conceptualized a comeback show for Anand Seth where the photographer showcased photographs of 10 leading women. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_anandseth_show"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Preserving Memories: The New Indian Express</h4> <p class=thin>20th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Even as the ongoing economic slowdown may have affected the business sentiment and expansion plans of many companies, Canvera Digital Technologies is bullish about its future. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_newsindianexpress"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Freeze moments: The Statesmen </h4> <p class=thin>20th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Expressions and memories fade. So, memorable moments have to be captured and locked into albums for posterity. How did you look like three, twelve, eighteen, thirty or more. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_freezeMoments"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Now Get Yourself a Coffee Table Album: The Pioneer</h4> <p class=thin>18th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>How many times have you picked up a coffee table book at the bookstore and marveled at its design, picture quality layout and the grand way the subject matter is dealt with? Now can get the whole experience personalized - have the pictures and experiences of your wedding, traveling, wildlife tour, adventure trip - any moment you want to cherish, recorded in a form of coffee table book, or better still a coffee table album.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_pioneer_180809"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Innovative Photo Gifting Concepts: Wedding Affair</h4> <p class=thin>August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Canvera has introduced innovative photo gifting concepts with beautiful and international award winning coffee table books, memory books and calendars for weddings. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_weddingaffair"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Giving the photo call: Business Standard</h4> <p class=thin>10th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>One fine morning in 2006, Dhiraj Kacker received a phone call that changed his life as an employee with a successful start-up in the Silicon Valley. At the other end was his buddy Peeyush Rai coaxing him to come back to India to start their own business. And, Kacker didn't think twice.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_businesstandard_160909"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Framed, For Life</h4> <p class=thin>10th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Marriages are made in heaven, but weddings happen here on earth, and memories of the wondrous occasions are relived over and over again through pictures - whether black and white or, as they are today, as elaborated as the wedding itself.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_HT_chandigarh"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Photo Glossy</h4> <p class=thin>9th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com., an online digital photography company, promises to present your photos in a coffee-table book. You can have your book ready within 48 hours of having placed the order, says the organisers. <a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_hindu"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Announces Opening of its Kolkata Office </h4> <p class=thin>4th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com, India's fastest growing online digital photography company, announces the opening of its sales office in Kolkata. This is Canvera's 7th sales office in the country. The office will be headed by Arunava Chaudhuri who joined Canvera after stints with Reliance Money & ICICI in various sales capacities.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=Canvera_news_hindu"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Minibook review by Asian Photography</h4> <p class=thin>4th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>"I feel they [Canvera] are the best. Things are best left to the professionals"<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/downloadData.do?downloadContent=Canvera_MiniBookReview_AsianPhotography_June2009.pdf"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Supplement on Canvera with Better Photography's</h4> <p class=thin>June 2009</p> <p class=thin>Bring Your Most Precious Memories to Life with Canvera's Lightweight Coffee-table Books<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/downloadData.do?downloadContent=Canvera_supplement_BetterPhotography_June2009.pdf"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Wins Asia Pacific & Japan Award 2nd Year in a Row</h4> <p class=thin>15th May 2009</p> <p class=thin>Canvera. com, India's fastest growing online digital photography company, was given the Best Photobook prize for the second year in a row at the recently concluded Asia-Pacific & Japan HP Digital Print Award 2009 in Beijing, China. The photobook category attracted more than 50 entries from the APJ region.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=bestPhotobook09"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera Announces Opening of Ahmedabad Office</h4> <p class=thin>28th August 2009</p> <p class=thin>Canvera.com, India's fastest growing online digital photography company, announces the opening of its sales office in Ahmedabad. This is Canvera's 6th sales office in the country. This office will serve as the hub to serve the entire Gujarat market.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=news_ahmedabad"><sp