o Book/Coffee Table Book segment at the Asia Pacific and Japan HP Digital Print Awards 2008. The award was instituted to recognise outstanding achievements and innovations in print and packaging across Asia.<a href="https://www.canvera.com/web/99600846/staticContentAction.do?contentPage=bestPhotobook08"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Photo expo grabs eye balls: The Hindu</h4> <p class=thin>5th July 2008</p> <p class=thin>It was indeed a shutterbug's paradise at the 'Photo Expo and Sign Show 2008' and 'Broadcast and Film Expo 2008' that was held at People's Plaza, Necklace Road on Friday. <a href=http://www.hindu.com/2008/07/05/stories/2008070558530200.htm><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="row info"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Online photo printing startups target pros: LiveMint</h4> <p class=thin>20th June 2008</p> <p class=thin>Late last year, Palak Jhaveri, owner of Sanat Jhaveri and Co., a photo studio in Ahmedabad, was grappling with a six-year-old problem. Ever since the 50-year old studio had taken to digital photography in 2001, Jhaveri had been facing "deep trouble storing wedding photos".<a href=http://www.livemint.com/2008/06/30234646/Online-photo-printing-startup.html><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a></p> </div> </div> <div class="row info last"> <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3"> <div class="icon logo"></div> </div> <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"> <h4>Canvera raises Series A Funding from Footprint, DFJ & umbai Angels: Content Sutra</h4> <p class=thin>5th May 2008</p> <p class=thin>Canvera, a Bangalore-based digital photo startup has raised an undisclosed amount of funding in a round led by Footprint Ventures, reports VC Circle. The Series A round also included Draper Fisher Jurvetson, Mumbai Angels and two angel investors from the UK. With a desktop application... <a href="http://www.contentsutra.com/entry/419-canvera-raises-series-a-funding-from-footprint-dfj-and-mumbai-angels/"><span class="thin read">Read More</span></a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration=500ms data-wow-delay=0s> <div class=canvera-twitter> <a class=twitter-timeline href=https://twitter.com/canvera data-widget-id=659686168389287936>Tweets by @canvera</a> </div> <div id=loading-div-twitter style="position: absolute;background-color: #f2f2f2;top: 0px;left: 15px;right: 14px;bottom: 0px">Loading...</div> </div> <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration=500ms data-wow-delay=0s> <div class=canvera-facebook> <div id=fb-root></div> <div class=fb-page data-href=https://www.facebook.com/canvera data-small-header=false data-adapt-container-width=true data-hide-cover=false data-show-facepile=true data-show-posts=true> <div class=fb-xfbml-parse-ignore> <blockquote cite=https://www.facebook.com/canvera><a href=https://www.facebook.com/canvera>Canvera</a></blockquote> </div> </div> </div> <div id=loading-div-fb style="position: absolute;background-color: #f2f2f2;top: 0px;left: 15px;right: 14px;bottom: 0px"></div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </div> <!-- Footer template --> <footer id=footer> <div class=container> <h3>Contact Us</h3> <div class=row> <div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12 footer-add"> <p><a href=mailto:care@canvera.com>care@canvera.com</a></p> <p>1-800-419-0570</p> <p>Whatsapp : +91-7337778282</p> <p>#36/5, Ground Floor, 27th Main Road,AGR Industrial Area, Near DHL Courier Services. Somasundara Palya,Bengaluru (560102), Karnataka, India</p> </div> <div class="col-sm-5 col-xs-12 footer-links"> <ul> <li class=first> <a href="downloads" onclick=trackEventFooter(this.id) id=downloads-footer>Downloads</a> </li> <li> <a href="about" onclick=trackEventFoot